Moore headed home in the 74th minute to cancel out Breel Embolo's headed opener at the other end, which had come just after half-timeSwitzerland pressed on in five minutes of injury time and Gavranovic was denied another potential winner, this time Ward saving with his finger tipsThe draw comes after Italy beat Turkey 3-0 in the same group in the tournament's opening match in Rome on Friday